parameters:
\SE[2]Something feels a little off over there...? \SE[3]Look,
there was something at the bottom of the hole, a strange
world....

\SE[2]Well, there's no point in just talking about it.
\!\SE[3]Let's ask if we can meet this witch or something.

You're here for an outpatient visit, right? Please show me your
examination card and insurance card.

\SE[17]I-I have a request...? \SE[8]Um, we... want to meet the
witch....

So you're requesting a diagnosis from the doctor. Alright, please
wait a moment while I confirm the schedule...

Well then, Miss Laura. Since I have made an appointment for you,
please come again in 5 years.

\SE[76]F-Five years later...!? \!\SE[65]Do I really have to wait
that long...!?

Patients from all over the world are waiting for the treatment of
the doctor....

\SE[14]Oh no, what should we do...? Waiting for 5 years might be
a little too long, don't you think...?

\SE[4]It seems like my name is more well-known than I
expected.... \!\SE[75]It appears that there might be a real deal
after all....

\SE[60]I can't wait that long.... \.Is there any way we can do
something about it....

Good job. Next is the examination for Meria-chan starting at 2
o'clock.

'Teacher': \SE[0]Yes, thank you very much. \SE[1]Please also
prepare the antibiotics that I requested.
\SE[2] (By the way, I was being called Teacher just now, right?)
\SE[4] (So, does that mean she's a witch?)

\SE[64]Um... Excuse me...!! \SE[24]There's someone I want you to
see...!! \SE[64]They haven't woken up for a long time... That's
why...!!

\SE[64]I've been bedridden for 3 years already...!!
\!\SE[46]Please...! Please help me...!!

Teacher...! Meria-chan's condition has suddenly worsened! Please
come and see her immediately!!

\SE[22]Hey... calm down! \SE[19]If you keep acting like this, you
won't be able to see them...!

\SE[8]That's right.... \!\SE[9]We need to calm down for a
moment....

\SE[29]... Sorry, I was a little out of it. \SE[65] I'll go cool
my head for a bit...

\SE[74]It's finally a chance after 3 years.... \!\SE[51]She
couldn't stay calm from her perspective.

\SE[2]But what should we do? \!\SE[3]If we wait for 5 years,
Lunaroa will become an old lady...
